---
title: Chermoula Chickpea & Pumpkin Buddha Bowl with Leafy Greens, Quick-Pickled Cabbage & Garlic Sauce
description: This bowl full of nourishment will leave you feeling satisfied and energised in equal measure. Between crunchy
cabbage, roasted pumpkin and tasty chickpeas, every bite is a delight. Our favourite flourish is the dressing of
rich garlic dip drizzled on top.
